<div id="Idea_3870"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3870-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3870">Use Public Zero-Based Budgeting&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8094-4049">jbristor</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">All budget line-items should be reviewed, justified, then prioritized in order of importance.  The entire process (except national security items) should be available on the web for public review, comment, and input during the entire budgetary process. </div>
